* var_access.sno
* Bottleneck: identifier lookup — IdentifierTable[symbol] on every read/write.
* Reads and writes 5 distinct variables in a tight loop (2000 iters).
    A = 1
    B = 2
    C = 0
    D = 0
    E = 0
    N = 0
LOOP    A = A + 1
    B = B + 2
    C = A + B
    D = C + A
    E = D + B
    N = LT(N, 2000) N + 1               :S(LOOP)
    OUTPUT = E
END
